---
/**
 * Rows — a vertical list of two-column rows, each rendered by `Row`: a heading
 * (plus optional blurb/CTA) on the left and a block of content on the right,
 * stacking on narrow screens. Rows are separated by hairline dividers.
 */
---

<div class="rows">
  <slot />
</div>

<style>
  .rows {
    max-width: 52rem;
  }
</style>
